Dialogue: 69,0:00:05.69,0:00:08.49,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,Looks like it's day 4 of the Reapers' Game.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.83,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,What changes if we survive all 4 days? {Pronoun changed from I to we}
Dialogue: 69,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.79,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,I have no idea what will change if we do,
Dialogue: 69,0:00:18.79,0:00:21.17,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,but I don't want to give up.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:22.13,0:00:23.34,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:25.96,0:00:26.80,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,My dream.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.02,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,Shibuya's so diverse. You can really see all walks of life.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:05.65,0:02:08.02,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,I hate Shibuya.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:08.36,0:02:11.28,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,It's a cacophony of self-absorbed people in their own world. {Everyone's always making a ruckus whenever they please. Everyone pretends like no one else can hear them. It's a cacaphony of people in their own little worlds.}
Dialogue: 69,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.53,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,They're just like Noise.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.16,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Yo! This is where y'all were hangin', huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:19.16,0:02:21.79,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,The walls over by Ten-Four are gone today!
Dialogue: 69,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.54,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,Beat! Rhyme!
Dialogue: 69,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.71,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Everywhere else is still blocked, though,
Dialogue: 69,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.59,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Anyways whatcha guys up to?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.42,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Seems like you two are homies now.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.76,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,We are not.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:34.76,0:02:37.05,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,We were people-watching.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:37.05,0:02:40.10,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Oh. That scanning shit freaks me out, y'know?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.06,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Y'know, all those people out there, thinkin' different things.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.06,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:45.06,0:02:49.07,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Its a blur of values and opinions clashing with each other out there. {It's like a battleground where people's values clash with each other at a crazy rate. -- It's a melting pot of clashing values.}
Dialogue: 69,0:02:49.36,0:02:54.82,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,But y'know? Even though Shibuya's this crowded, nobody notices us.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:54.82,0:02:55.86,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.62,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,It makes me feel kinda lonely.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:57.62,0:02:58.95,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:59.53,0:03:00.99,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,In the Underground,
Dialogue: 69,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.00,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,I'm unconcerned about being noticed. {This + next line is said in passive form, which implies that he doesn't want people to notice him or talk to him, it's verbose but I added something that I thought would convey that. Without it, I think you can interpret these lines differently in English} {CPS is yeesh -TM}
Dialogue: 69,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.46,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,Nor about people trying to talk to me, either.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:06.00,0:03:08.92,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,I'm fine with not having to talk to anyone.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:09.50,0:03:13.30,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Y'know, you jus' said some real depressin' shit.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.38,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Ya good?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.47,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,Yeah. I just think it's useless talking to strangers. {Alternatively; Yeah. There's no point in talking to strangers.}
Dialogue: 69,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.56,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,I can see what someone's thinking just by scanning them.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:21.56,0:03:22.52,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,It's convenient.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:23.31,0:03:27.44,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,There's something... lonely about that.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:27.81,0:03:32.57,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,I think that you should first try to understand people by listening to what they have to say, though. {I actually think she's taking a jab at Neku here, so the "you" pronoun is important here since it can be interpreted as both general & direct advice}
Dialogue: 69,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.15,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:35.15,0:03:35.86,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.82,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Your stuffed animal's adorable.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:39.62,0:03:40.45,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,You mean Mr. Mew?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.78,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Mr. Mew?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.45,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,Yeah. I made him.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.12,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,Wanna touch him?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:46.12,0:03:46.83,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 69,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.67,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 69,0:03:48.67,0:03:51.13,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Mmm! He's so soft and fluffy!
Dialogue: 69,0:03:51.13,0:03:52.96,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,You're incredible, Shiki!
Dialogue: 69,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.63,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,I made this outfit, too.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?{&&& this is both beat and neku, so could we do something with that here?}
Dialogue: 69,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.59,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.47,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Word.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.68,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a fashion designer. {Liberal, but works better with the next line}
Dialogue: 69,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.52,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,That's a great dream.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:05.52,0:04:09.19,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,I'm jealous. I don't really know what it's like to have a dream. {The "I'm jealous" bit is implied in JP since she trails her sentence off but I made it explicit in the TL}
Dialogue: 69,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.27,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,You "don't know"? Doesn't that just mean that you don't have one? {I feel like snapping to kf makes the line end too early - Laffer}
Dialogue: 69,0:04:13.73,0:04:14.69,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,The hell! Phones! {Not cool, Phones! might work better here}
Dialogue: 69,0:04:14.69,0:04:17.11,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Watch your temper, Beat! {This is actually a very good TL, don't touch this one}
Dialogue: 69,0:04:20.78,0:04:27.54,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Listen, Rhyme. You'll find a dream someday as long as you just keep movin' forward!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.04,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Who cares if you ain't got one right now?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.13,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,As for me, I'm gonna be the best skateboarder in the world!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:37.13,0:04:37.92,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,True!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.30,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Someday, I'll find a dream of my own.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.64,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,Isn't that pendant really rare?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.77,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,I stood in line with friends for hours, but I still missed out.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:48.14,0:04:52.06,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,It was a birthday present from my big brother.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.73,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,Wow. You've got a great brother.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.65,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.15,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,He's super nice.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.11,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,I'm really proud of him.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.62,Default,Pedestrian,0,0,0,,{\an8}I hear there's an event at Ten-Four!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.41,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:05.83,0:05:06.99,Default,Pedestrian,0,0,0,,Hey, you hear that?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.70,Default,Pedestrian,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.46,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,Hey, what's with all the hustlin' outta nowhere? {Alternatively: Hey, what's all the commotion about?}
Dialogue: 69,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.83,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,It seems like they're all going towards Ten-Four.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.46,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,Well, the mission hasn't arrived yet, so... y'all wanna check it out?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.63,Default,Beat,0,0,0,,I ain't interested if it ain't a mission.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.97,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Oh, slow down, Beat!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.26,Default,Rhyme,0,0,0,,Sorry. See you around.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:29.06,0:05:30.77,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,There they go.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:30.77,0:05:32.06,Default,Shiki,0,0,0,,What about you, Neku?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.44,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,I'm keen if you are.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.99,Default,Neku,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's with this crowd?!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:41.99,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty normal for Ten-Four.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There's new styles on display!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! These are so totally cute.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eri, what do you...?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eri?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:56.13,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 69,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to come here a lot with friends.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oji!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiji!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell's that guy?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Eiji Oji.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:09.60,0:06:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,His don't-give-a-damn attitude helped him become a huge star recently.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn they're loud. {Alternatively, "What a ruckus."}
Dialogue: 69,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All he did was drink water, right?!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,People like to say, "The Prince sells."
Dialogue: 69,0:06:25.45,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that Eiji Oji shills sells out in a flash.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:30.33,0:06:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That pendant Rhyme had, he plugged on his blog.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:33.79,0:06:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That one you said you stood in line for, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I'm a bit of a fan.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:39.17,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to fashion, his comments have always been a hit.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:43.30,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, those clothes you're wearing, you said you made them?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you bought them.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:49.18,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I only did the sewing. The designs are Eri's.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:53.73,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to make clothes.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:57.19,0:07:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want lots of people to wear our clothes.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want people to be happy wearing them.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?{&&&can we have the subs pop up like That... (pause) so?}
Dialogue: 69,0:07:06.99,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, mind if I take a look at the shop back there?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:10.95,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.{Does anyone actually reply to "Do you mind?" with "No?" - is it just me that's the weird one?}{sometimes I do reply "I do mind" but it depends on context.}
Dialogue: 69,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is that why you're trying so hard?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you survive these seven days,
Dialogue: 69,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,will your dream come true?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Free Spain Hill from the Noise"?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:35.81,0:07:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!{&&& can't think of anything else here}
Dialogue: 69,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no end to 'em!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the Noise is being attracted to someone?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Neku! Those two!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad at me, Ai?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you already, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies! You're 100% mad at me!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think im lying?!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's so much Noise!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How do things even get{\i1} this{\i0} bad?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the Noise are swarming to those two.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:07.22,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Noise keeps coming, no matter how many we erase.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Neku, can you deal with the Noise around them for me?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha! I'm on it!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:35.37,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are these two fighting?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:37.58,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she's hiding it.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:40.29,0:08:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that she's been meeting with Makoto.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:45.34,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah shit. I'm pretty sure Ai's got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:49.09,0:08:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to surprise her might've backfired.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:52.55,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to try Imprinting.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:57.48,0:09:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,, It's using your Player pin to \Ndirectly speak to someone's mind.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:03.69,0:09:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, talk to each other and resolve this.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:11.61,0:09:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you and Makoto have been meeting together in private!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:16.79,0:09:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess the cat's outta the bag then, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you act so calm when—?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What're these?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try changing the subject!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:26.88,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You two wanted go, right? To see 777's concert. {Mistranslated in original TL}
Dialogue: 69,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been saying you wanted to see it, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:34.14,0:09:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Makoto and I were trying to surprise you for your birthday.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A surprise?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, I should've trusted you!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy getting these tickets, you know.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mina!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Neku! The Noise has stopped spawning!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:55.66,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just gotta clean up the stragglers now!{Alternatively; "Just have to clean these ones up, now"}
Dialogue: 69,0:10:07.00,0:10:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lets go!
Dialogue: 69,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 69,0:10:32.28,0:10:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Looks like I owe you a treat.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}For real? I want a parfait, then.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:37.95,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You got it!
Dialogue: 69,0:10:34.74,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like those two managed to make up.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:40.74,0:10:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:42.41,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends help each other whether they're sad or in trouble, and...
Dialogue: 69,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whatcha' doin' later, Eri?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not too sure yet.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's go that way, Neku.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:51.84,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:52.92,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You haven't mentioned that girl lately.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Let's just go.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Shiki.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:04.35,0:11:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl, she looks just like you!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are... kind of complicated.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let me know if you \Nneed someone to talk to.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:12.74,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's because... in here... {Here refers to the UG}
Dialogue: 69,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm Eri.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at day 5 already, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you doing okay?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not be much help today.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much help? What's wrong—?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:38.22,0:11:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Monopolize the Scramble Crossing view at 3:00."
Dialogue: 69,0:11:41.89,0:11:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Monopolize the view"?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:43.35,0:11:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hours from now?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem possible, it's simply not enough time!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Makoto. \NI'm counting on you to make it work
Dialogue: 69,0:11:51.77,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already scheduled the ad to be played on the big screen at 3 P.M.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:56.32,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you set it up so that everyone's eyes are locked on the screen for me, please?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:00.95,0:12:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But if we just play the video, everyone will walk right by it.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, could that be today's mission?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was spacing out.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that girl we passed by?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:20.89,0:12:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Eri. The one I told you about.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:24.68,0:12:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cute, and smart, and everyone likes her.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:29.40,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I... wished I could be her.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes no sense to me.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:40.78,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you wanted to cheer people up with the clothes you made?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 69,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiki.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:51.67,0:12:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're fine just the way you are.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's clear this mission.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But how exactly are we gonna clear this mission?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:08.52,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We use Eiji Oji.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will listen if it comes from his mouth.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This water's totes delicious.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:14.86,0:13:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prince knows his stuff!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:16.86,0:13:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's that water from yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:19.53,0:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. We might learn something about Oji if we scan them.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's just water, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I only got it because you waited in line for me, Sota.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm like, super happy now.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}R-Really?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sota.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:29.04,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Oji's holding an event at AMX later.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're giving out all of these?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:37.09,0:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher ups are pressuring me to spread 'em around.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside...
Dialogue: 69,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...these things look like red skulls.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's there another wall here?!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already short on time!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:52.56,0:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what we have to do to open it.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no Noise around, either.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The requirements have been met.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wall clear.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The wall's gone.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forth. Keep that pin safe.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:13.21,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:18.17,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to "keep that pin safe", right?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:21.84,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There was light coming out of my pocket just now.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:25.09,0:14:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What pins do I have that you don't?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably that pin you got from that Reaper— the one in the band.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(16,308,\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Oh, that one!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, 777 is a Reaper, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that means some Reapers are good guys.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:42.69,0:14:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why've you got two Player pins, Neku?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:47.49,0:14:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Player Pins are supposed to be one per person.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:50.66,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know? I don't even know why I'm playing this game.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, umm...
Dialogue: 69,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Having two might come in handy!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:00.13,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, if you put the spare pin in your chest pocket, it might stop a bullet, or something!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you're back to normal. {Alternatively; "Thats more like the Shiki I know."}
Dialogue: 69,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Neku, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for today!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night,
Dialogue: 69,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lost in thought, drinking this delicious water, {Thirst-quenching can replace delicious here}
Dialogue: 69,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,when it hit me.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Skull pins!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:38.88,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if you all put these on, I wonder?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:44.47,0:15:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it'd be the birth of a new trend!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:48.18,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everybody! Let's start a trend together!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:51.10,0:15:51.89,Alt,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to use Imprinting.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the giant screen on Q Front at 3 p.m.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:00.65,0:16:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you all to put on the Red Skull pins,
Dialogue: 69,0:16:02.52,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and then go watch the giant screen at Q Front at 3 p.m.!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be our little date. {Yakusoku literally means "promise" but it has a connotation of meeting up with someone at a given place or time, and the reason why all the girls scream here is because it has this connotation of a date}
Dialogue: 69,0:16:17.16,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch the giant screen at Scramble Crossing  at 3 p.m. today!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The crowd's started to grow.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it worked.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:28.47,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh! Makoto!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? Ai?
Dialogue: 69,0:16:33.93,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Those girls are...
Dialogue: 69,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,1024)}Hi there. {Makoto says "Why are you—" but it's like the third subtitle here so you're gonna have to deal with it somehow}
Dialogue: 69,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1400,1024)}Why are you— {:thinking: -Laffer}
Dialogue: 69,0:16:34.89,0:16:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. She found out about the surprise, and... {Removed the italics because that sounds mega condescending}
Dialogue: 69,0:16:38.27,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for them.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Two birds with one stone again.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 3 p.m.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:03.34,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that thing?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a Noise?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:15.31,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, no one warned me about that thing!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't enough to clear the mission?!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no use.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for. {Alternatively; We're going to get erased.}
Dialogue: 69,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 69,0:18:01.27,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...just happened?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we cleared the mission.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:07.15,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So... we're safe for now?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't normal, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:14.16,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of other Players got erased too.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:17.53,0:18:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One wrong move, and we'd have joined them.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been saving my neck all day, Neku.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get it together.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:29.13,0:18:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're doing more than enough.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved that part-timer from back then,
Dialogue: 69,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and stopped those schoolgirls fighting yesterday—
Dialogue: 69,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we've made it this far because you didn't abandon anyone.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(848,1140,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Plus...
Dialogue: 69,0:18:45.44,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...you didn't give up on me, even after what I did.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:49.40,0:18:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people have been saved 'cause of something that you did.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:53.78,0:18:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're pretty... {phrasing  is ???}
Dialogue: 69,0:18:56.99,0:18:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...incredible.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Neku.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:02.37,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you've changed quite a lot\Nin such a short space of time.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:05.87,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 69,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...never want to screw up like that again.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you'll be fine, Neku.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem down today, Eri. You okay?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:24.56,0:19:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I know we're here to have fun.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do have something on your mind. Talk to me.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:30.90,0:19:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:32.15,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 69,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of giving up designing completely.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! You're so good at it!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eri, why?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:43.37,0:19:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna know, just scan her.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:45.29,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could ever do something like that.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:48.83,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I loved the outfit you showed me the other day.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:52.09,0:19:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want to see more of your designs.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel like I'd be intruding on my friend's thoughts.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like she'll know.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thanks.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overcomplicating things. {He says "It's simple, isn't it?" with the implied meaning that I left in the TL}
Dialogue: 69,0:19:56.68,0:19:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:58.26,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought of finding out what Eri really thought of me...
Dialogue: 69,0:20:02.89,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...scares me.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:05.81,0:20:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say your dream was to be a fashion designer?
Dialogue: 69,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it without Shiki.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiki's incredible.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:16.03,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She turns the smallest ideas into complete items.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:19.32,0:20:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's skilled, considerate, and a hard worker.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:23.54,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she had more talent than me.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:26.75,0:20:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't find the right way to tell her.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hurt her.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:31.84,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, Shiki was worrying that she wasn't good at designing clothes.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:37.17,0:20:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"You don't have to be a designer", was what I wanted to tell her. {Alternatively, "You should do what you do best", was what I wanted to say.}
Dialogue: 69,0:20:41.89,0:20:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But what came out was: "You're not meant to be a designer."
Dialogue: 69,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're a great seamstress, anyways."
Dialogue: 69,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologise right away.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:51.40,0:20:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to say sorry first thing the next morning.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 69,0:20:59.24,0:21:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can never see her again.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:05.04,0:21:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The clothes I design only become real when Shiki makes them for me.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 69,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't do it without Shiki.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:17.59,0:21:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... how she thought of me? {Not phrased like a question in JP but rhetorical because she's talking to herself out of disbelief}
Dialogue: 69,0:21:20.68,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was our dream
Dialogue: 69,0:21:22.59,0:21:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to make lots of people happy with the clothes we made together,
Dialogue: 69,0:21:28.02,0:21:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but now...
Dialogue: 69,0:21:30.52,0:21:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now... it still {\i1}is{\i0} our dream. {Present tense italicised to emphasise that the dream is not dead}
Dialogue: 69,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Neku, I'm sure now.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:39.61,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to come back to life and make clothes with Eri.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? "Come back to life"?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember that either.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Reapers' Game.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:51.67,0:21:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My entry fee was my appearance.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really look like I do now.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:58.96,0:22:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how Eri looks.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:02.18,0:22:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 69,0:22:03.93,0:22:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reapers' Game is where Players are assessed\Nto see who deserves a second chance at life.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I died in an accident.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:11.98,0:22:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm...
Dialogue: 69,0:22:15.61,0:22:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 69,0:22:17.82,0:22:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...dead?!
Dialogue: 69,0:23:52.58,0:23:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "Erased."
